<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Nov 2021 13:29:15 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>BMW iX 旗艦純電 SAV 抵港，豪華高科技車廂逐格睇</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/KDetNdxUQQo/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 10 Nov 2021 13:17:44 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[BMW iX]]></category><category><![CDATA[sav]]></category><category><![CDATA[純電動車]]></category><category><![CDATA[電動車]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070639</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>BMW 早於 2013 年就推出 BMW i3 純電動車與 BMW i8 混能跑車，而在今年他們將正式推出純電 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>BMW 早於 2013 年就推出 BMW i3 純電動車與 BMW i8 混能跑車，而在今年他們將正式推出純電旗艦 SAV BMW iX。此車為純電車款，配以豪華車廂內裝。BMW iX 最近就到了香港，等記者同大家到場睇清楚這部旗艦車的真身！</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070670" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070671" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>作為旗艦款式純電車款，當然不能錯過它的外觀與車廂內籠設計。車頭注目的雙腎型鬼面罩嵌入智慧面板，它內置了攝影機與雷達系統，而且經得起刮傷考驗，於室溫 24 小時內或暖流 5 分鐘內自行修復。車身採用 0.25Cd 低風阻設計，而作為旗艦款整個車架亦特別為 BMW iX 重新設計，令座艙空間大大提升。車架以碳纖複合物作為主要物料，配以鋁合金製造而成。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0022-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070672" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0022-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0022-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0022-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0022-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070673" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0018.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070674" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0018-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0018-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0018-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0018.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/P90422861_highRes_bmw-gen5-powertrain--scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/P90422861_highRes_bmw-gen5-powertrain--694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/P90422861_highRes_bmw-gen5-powertrain--694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/P90422861_highRes_bmw-gen5-powertrain--1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/P90422861_highRes_bmw-gen5-powertrain--768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/P90422861_highRes_bmw-gen5-powertrain--1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/P90422861_highRes_bmw-gen5-powertrain--2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/P90422861_highRes_bmw-gen5-powertrain--scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>BMW iX 車廂內籠以「生活空間」為主題，車廂物料選用了天然鞣製的真皮皮革、FSC 認證木材、100% 再生尼龍質料腳踏墊等天然與回收材料。BMW iX 提供 3 種車廂風格內裝包括 Atelier、Loft 及 Suit，標配的 Atelier 內裝可選擇三種顏色，包括白色﹑黑色及深啡色。而 Loft 內裝標準配備以布料及纖維質料組成的藍灰色內籠設計，Suite 內裝則以橄欖葉分泌處理的皮革製作全車坐椅，加上金色飾件﹑對比縫線及透氣孔。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0020-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070678" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-3-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-3-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>BMW iX 亦把科技融入到車廂之中，包括應用了納米纖維濾芯空氣過濾技術﹑加入隱藏式 Head-up Display 投射功能，為前座多功能座椅提供按摩功能等。前座坐椅的中空頭枕，更嵌入了多個隱形揚聲器，整體感觀更加簡潔俐落。前兩個座位之間的中空設計，令乘客有更多伸展空間。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070641" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>中控台控制台用上 Clear &amp; Bold 玻璃切割內飾組件，iDrive 控制器嵌上玻璃觸控旋轉按鈕，波棍亦換上玻璃轉檔撥片，音量控制器換上玻璃滾輪及以玻璃飾件製作的前座座位調較按鈕，並加入了主動震動回饋和觸控功能，取代傳統按鈕。<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-mc-interior-features-01.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-mc-interior-features-01-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-mc-interior-features-01-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-mc-interior-features-01-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-mc-interior-features-01-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-mc-interior-features-01-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-mc-interior-features-01.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0014-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0014-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0014-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0014-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0014-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070668" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011-3-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011-3-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0011-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>BMW iX 亦主打 Shy Tech 隱形創新科技，除在 BMW 雙腎型鬼面罩融入了鏡頭、雷達、感應器和加熱元件，更在車頭的徽章隱藏了雨潑水的注水口；隱藏式門柄﹑車內則有音響系統的隱形嵌入式揚聲器和獨特按鈕設計。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>BMW iX 採用 BMW eDrive 技術以及電動四輪驅動設計，eDrive 動力技術包括兩組電動摩打、電子系統和充電技術。BMW iX 電池容量達 71 – 105 kWh，BMW iX xDrive40 標準配備 21 吋雙色輕合金輪圈；電動馬達能夠輸出最大馬力 326hp，峰值扭力達 630Nm，0 至 100 公里／小時僅需 6.1 秒，續航能力長達 425km。而 BMW iX xDrive50 標準配備 22 吋雙色輕合金輪圈，整合式主動轉向系統及雙軸式氣壓懸掛系統；電動馬達能夠輸出最大馬力 523hp，峰值扭力達 765Nm，0 至 100 公里／小時僅需 4.6 秒，續航能力為 630km。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-ms-range.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-ms-range-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-ms-range-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-ms-range-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/bmw-x-series-ix-ms-range.jpg 890w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>BMW iX 更支援 BMW Digital Key 電子車匙功能，透過 NFC 晶片感應就能夠取替實體車匙，手提電話可當作為車匙使用，只需把手提電話輕輕放在車門手柄即可解鎖, 將手提電話放在無線充電座上便能啟動車輛。電子車匙更可分享給最多 5 位朋友。</p><h2>規格與香港車價</h2><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="top">BMW 電動車型號</td><td valign="top">BMW iX xDrive40</td><td valign="top">BMW iX xDrive50</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">電池容量 (kWh)</td><td valign="top">71</td><td valign="top">105</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">最高續航力 (km)　(WLTP)</td><td valign="top">425</td><td valign="top">630</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">最大馬力 (hp)</td><td valign="top">326</td><td valign="top">523</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">最大扭力 (Nm)</td><td valign="top">630</td><td valign="top">765</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">0-100 km/h 加速 (s)</td><td valign="top">6.1</td><td valign="top">4.6</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">車重 (kg)</td><td valign="top">2,440</td><td valign="top">2,585</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">車身，長 x 闊 x 高 (mm)</td><td valign="top">4953 x 1967 x 1695</td><td valign="top"></td></tr><tr><td valign="top">一換一後售價 (HKD$)</td><td valign="top">798,000 起</p><p>（售價：＄988,000 起）</td><td valign="top">1,088,000 起</p><p>（售價：1,278,000 起）</td></tr></tbody></table></p><div class="feedflare">
