p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-579x580.jpeg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-579x580.jpeg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-899x900.jpeg 899w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-768x769.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA.jpeg 1130w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BF859B50-3E58-49E6-A648-1F31DA70890F-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BF859B50-3E58-49E6-A648-1F31DA70890F-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BF859B50-3E58-49E6-A648-1F31DA70890F-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BF859B50-3E58-49E6-A648-1F31DA70890F.jpeg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070562" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC-531x580.jpeg" alt="" width="531" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC-531x580.jpeg 531w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC-824x900.jpeg 824w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC-768x839.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC.jpeg 1153w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 531px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">遊戲官方網站已註明玩家可免費將測試資格轉讓給朋友或是熟人，但不能販賣或轉售測試資格，因此炒賣是官方嚴禁的行為。港台繁中版的抽選結果就在今日公佈。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：</span><a href="https://jp.mercari.com/item/m33601422747"><span style="font-weight: 400;">mercari</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
